{"words":[{"mot":"ROSTAND","col":"1","line":"2","direction":"V","def1":"","def2":"Edmond Rostand. L`auteur."},{"mot":"BALCON","col":"4","line":"1","direction":"V","def1":"","def2":"Caché dans l'ombre,  Cyrano souffle à Christian, sous le balcon de Roxane, sa déclaration d'amour."},{"mot":"LETTRES","col":"9","line":"2","direction":"V","def1":"","def2":"Cyrano franchit régulièrement, au péril de sa vie, les lignes espagnoles pour faire parvenir à Roxane des lettres qu`il écrit et qu'il signe du nom de Christian."},{"mot":"ROXANE","col":"1","line":"2","direction":"H","def1":"","def2":""},{"mot":"COUVENT","col":"3","line":"5","direction":"H","def1":"","def2":"Roxane, retirée au couvent, réalise qu'alors qu'elle croyait aimer Christian, c?est de Cyrano qu'elle était vraiment amoureuse."},{"mot":"NEZ","col":"1","line":"7","direction":"H","def1":"","def2":""},{"mot":"CADETS","col":"4","line":"8","direction":"H","def1":"","def2":"Christian, dont est éprise Roxanne, fait partie des \"cadets de Gascogne\", la compagnie de Cyrano."}],"theme":"Cyrano de Bergerac","letters":["T","O","N","R","V","L","C","A"]}